    rcxn:hasMeaning "The central senses of argument structure construction have been argued to be in association with humanly relevant scenes like: transferring [something]3 to [someone]3, causing [something]3 to change state or move, experiencing [something,]3 [something]1 undergoing a change of state or location" .

